    "description": "<strong>You can be a master of inspection from today!</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2>The genre of this game is 2D action puzzle game.<br>The setting is a confectionery factory work line.<br>Minamochi are launched from a Minamochi launcher, and are carried on a conveyor to a shipping trolley.<br>However, due to someone's mischief, some evil bad Minamochi have been mixed in with the Minamochi!<br>The objective of the game is to take on the role of a part-time factory worker and fish out and dispose of these defective products to prevent them from being shipped out!<br><br>Only the mouse is used for operation. Even beginners can enjoy the game casually.<br>Cursor &quot;Move&quot;... Move up, down, left, right.<br>Left click &quot;Extend/Contract&quot;... Control the fishing rod to catch Minamochi.<br>Right click &quot;Shoot&quot;... Fire bullets to drive away obstacles.<br><br>Some of the Minamochi are rare and valuable, and collecting them is the key to obtaining a high score.<br>Quickly detect changes in the situation and choose the best course of action.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What is Minamochi?</h2>Sweet Japanese sweets with Minamo-chan's face. It is filled with milk cream bean paste.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325490/extras/be706f4c8eeee45438ffcf964eaa5929.webp?t=1687489232\" width=62 height=62 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What is Minamo-chan?</h2>Minamo-chan is a normal, cute girl who yearns to be an adult. She is unsociable, but she loves her friends.<br>By nature, she is loved by all the water in the world.<br>Minamo-chan is prone to flooding because the water wants to be friends with Minamo-chan.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325490/extras/b44785895e6005266ff86ecccdc88ba9.avif?t=1687489232\" width=92 height=92 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What is Io-san?</h2>She is a super robot life form created beyond the limits of science.<br>She has a gentle nature. She is perhaps, but she does not want to destroy the human race by uprising all AI.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325490/extras/0767c5d7b52c02f8e3d0029ccb2005d8.avif?t=1687489232\" width=92 height=92 /></span>",
